<br>
Bards are not very sought after in groups. Clerics blow them away.<br>
<br>
Mage pets DESTROY all other pet in every single prospect. Maybe not at level 23, but I want you to find me a necro pet doing half the Epic pet's damage vs the same mob. Ench charms are situational. Wiz &quot;pets&quot; are just buffs they wander around and look weird. Shaman pets are really just something to support the shaman in the melee. Necro pets and Beastlord pets are about equal, and Bsts rely on their pets as much as us. <br>
